<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> إِلَّا:</span> سَرَاوِيلَ لِعَدَم إِزَارٍ، وَخُفَّيْنِ لِعَدَمِ نَعْلَيْنِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَالطِّيبُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَقَتْلُ صَيْدِ البَرِّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٧]</span> وَعَقْدُ نِكَاحٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٨]</span> وَجِمَاعٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٩]</span> وَمُبَاشَرَةٌ فِيمَا دُونَ فَرْجٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَفِي:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- أَقَلَّ مِنْ ثَلَاثِ شَعَرَاتٍ،<span class="c5"> وَثَلَاثَةِ أَظْفَارٍ:</span> فِي كُلِّ وَاحِدٍ فَأَقَلَّ طَعَامُ مِسْكِينٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَفِي الثَّلَاثِ فَأَكْثَرَ:</span> دَمٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَفِي تَغْطِيَةِ الرَّأْسِ بِلَاصِقٍ، وَلُبْسِ مَخِيطٍ، وَتَطَيُّبٍ فِي بَدَنٍ، أَوْ ثَوْبٍ، أَوْ شَمٍّ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ دَهْنٍ:</span> الفِدْيَةُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ قَتَلَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> صَيْداً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> مَأْكُولاً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> بَرِّيًّا أَصْلاً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَعَلَيْهِ جَزَاؤُهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>